Cell["\<\
We got number of roots, some of them are real, some of them is complex. But \
for tems of discontinuity real or complex values makes no difference they all \
cause discontinuities.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.766469331919967*^9, 3.766469356152112*^9}, {
   3.7664728623412857`*^9, 3.766472870363987*^9}, {3.7664731151065617`*^9, 
   3.7664731745746613`*^9}, {3.7664738307215*^9, 3.7664738999771185`*^9}, {
