Cell["\<\
Plots of Mathematica can not indicate the points where the function has type \
A discontinuity. We should not rely to the Mathematica plots on the subject, \
the final decision must be taken only after mathematical analysis. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7664743440103045`*^9, 3.7664745390954213`*^9}, 
   3.7668896034095893`*^9, {3.7668896359099627`*^9, 
