Cell["\<\
The limit examination with Mthematica, reveals that, limits in both \
directions in the discontinuity point x = 1, is Indeterminate in both \
sides.This indicates that the given function has an essential (unremovable) \
discontinuity named ``Discontinuity of the Second \
Kind\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] at the point x = 1.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7669244972305965`*^9, 3.7669246984120026`*^9}, 
   3.7669267242768764`*^9, {3.766969580169259*^9, 
   3.766969586623602*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f7480ddf-eef4-49da-bd52-\
9483b4f3bf8a"]
}, Open  ]],

