Cell["\<\
The function has a discontinuity of the second kind (non-removable jump \
discontiniuty) at x =0. At least one of the side limits should be \
indeterminate (complex infinity).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.766248944894206*^9, 3.766249090296961*^9}, {
  3.7663783790136423`*^9, 3.766378381245368*^9}, {3.766378411949832*^9, 
  3.7663784716617355`*^9}, {3.7664987930155005`*^9, 3.7664987942641134`*^9}, {
  3.766724045382427*^9, 
  3.766724047007683*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d563ee3a-11e4-4524-858d-\
fabd659f99b6"],

