Cell["\<\
Adding PlotLegends (added by default after the plot) ( they are also labeled \
by tooltips). Plot legends may be placed at \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Before\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote],\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]Above\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]\
,\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]Below\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] and \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]After\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] as ex. PlotLegends \
\[Rule] Placed[{\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]sin(x)\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote],\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]cos(x)\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote],After]. If \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]After is the choice, it is the default value and \
stating PlotLegends\[Rule] Expressions\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] will suffice.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7665722709598083`*^9, 3.766572333799763*^9}, {
  3.7665724977447224`*^9, 3.7665725279603915`*^9}, {3.7665743160528355`*^9, 
