Cell["\<\
It is strongly advisable to make a very basic plot of any function to be \
plotted, ther we can see what will its behavior and assess the domain and \
range intervals for a detailed plot.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.766749237103242*^9, 
  3.7667493832636523`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2689c339-f444-4b51-8c1d-\
67e972fca2d0"],

